content.rendered:
Directed by Gopichand Malineni

Written by Gopichand Malineni. Sai Madhav Burra. Gopichand Malineni

Cast Ravi Teja(Pothuraju Veera Shankar (as Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja)). Shruti Haasan(Kalyani (as Sruthi Hassan)). Sudhakar Komakula(Kiran). Samuthirakani(Katari Krishna (as Samudrakhani)). Varalaxmi Sarathkumar(Jayamma (as Varalakshmi Sarathkumar)). Vamsee Chaganti(SI Balaji (as Vamsi Chaaganti)). P. Ravi Shankar(Konda Reddy (as Ravi Shankar)). Mohammad Ali(Shankar’s Friend (as Ali)). Sathwik Malineni(Cheeku (as Master Sathwik)). Chirag Jani(Saleem Bhatkal (as Chiraag Johnny)). Priyanka Raman(Deepthi Bedi). Raghu Babu(MLA (as Raghubabu)). Hyper Aadi(Constable (as Hyper Adi)). Sapthagiri(Subba Reddy). Chandan((as Master Chandan)). Bhavika((as Baby Bhavika)). Jabardasth Appa Rao((as Jabardasth Apparao)). Saddhaam Adhirindhi((as Adhirindhi Saddhaam)). Apsara Rani(Item Girl in the Song ‘Bhoom Bhaddhal’). Stun Shiva(Ankadu (as Stunt Siva)).Anurag Chowdary.Chammak Chandra.Jabardasth Mahesh.Chitram Srinu.Josh Ravi. Mahesh Kathi(Kathi (as Kathi Mahesh)).Vargeesh. Devi Prasad(SI Tilak). Anish Kuruvilla(Commissioner).Goparaju Ramana.Vivek Anand. Racha Ravi((as Rachha Ravi)). Mouryani(Katari Nithya (as Mouryaani)).Praveena Reddy. Jeeva(Local Rowdy). Siva Akula((as Akula Siva)). B.V.S. Ravi(Bystander (as Machha Ravi)). 

Language Telugu

Producers Madhu B.. Ammiraju Kaanumilli.

Production Saraswathi Films Division
